Denise Benoît https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Denise_Beno%C3%AEt 0 Denise Benoît (10 September 1919 – 29 May 1973) was a French actress and singer, active across a wide range of genres on the stage, radio and television. Other members of her family were musicians.
